{"tid":1845994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】大S徐熙媛日本狂掃萬個口罩　汪小菲：今天寄往武漢","createTime":"2020-01-27T12:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T08:58:12.000Z","uid":209657,"like":5,"dislike":721,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"3f97c3bb938725fdb10b8b31ed2816e489f9cd48","tid":1845994,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3920255/org/f8ae952841b9315c9b1b6ec8c78ed173.JPG/u0ue-6EBnbXvuWmN00qmtEw2WR87CBKDZpLXkGaS15A?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3920255%2Forg%2Ff8ae952841b9315c9b1b6ec8c78ed173.JPG%2Fu0ue-6EBnbXvuWmN00qmtEw2WR87CBKDZpLXkGaS15A%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b6f18ed4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5349fb330fbdb7eb46e60d2b30cc589cf2c0ed7d","tid":1845994,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":87,"score":-86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:23:14.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情愈來愈嚴重，世界各地確診個案都不停上升當中，市民紛紛搶購口罩自保，台灣已經率先宣布，醫療外科口罩和N95停止出口一個月，優先供應台灣需求。大S徐熙媛近月忙於照顧仔女，原來佢私下默默行善，佢丈夫汪小菲呢日發微博話：「老婆在日本找到了一萬個口罩，今天寄往武漢。」<br />\n<br />\n內地湖北省多個市相繼封城，從流出視頻所知當地防疫用品供應相當緊張，大S雖然係台灣藝人，但嫁給來自內地嘅汪小菲後都相當關心疫情。呢日汪小菲發微博話：「老婆也是台灣人，她在日本找到了一萬個口罩，今天寄往武漢我的同學那邊，再麻煩他幫我們捐贈。陸續我們也會通過日本的管道找一些更專業的口罩。」"},{"pid":"0e7ba5f53640c7fb643e6454cfc410b64b3eb982","tid":1845994,"uid":254183,"like":267,"dislike":1,"score":266,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:23:29.000Z","msg":"跑到日本搶人口罩寄給支那<br />\n呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9424923f8f5f912e9a0ceb334f244691fb2e1cd","tid":1845994,"uid":209657,"like":9,"dislike":138,"score":-129,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3920271/org/dd5df3e27f8123e0890c4d0ce22f4f63.JPG/T1edFaHdVNnoPxWK0BorqeER-BgC-AtA7WvtBO1r7QQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk